distributed p2p communication platform targetting 
    reliable file transfers, messaging, audio and video
as one cross platform solution 

you are gonna need:
openssl 1.1.1d (important)
opus/libopus 1.3-1 or higher
cmake
make
gcc
libpq (optional, if building with server)

to build default (library, tests, clients):
    ./configure
    cd bin && make

to build server:
    ./configure
    cd bin && make server

to build and install library globally
    ./configure
    cd bin && make
    sudo make install
